taskadd DAYSTAMP "TASK"

DAYSTAMP must be one of three conditions
  yy/mm/dd     this is accepted specific format example 23/05/17  which is 17th May 2023
  today        when you type today, command will assume it the current date and adds task correctly
  tomorrow     when you type tomorrow, command will assume it the tomorrow date and adds task correctly
  
  "TASK"       Task must be covered with " "     example:  "learn more linux commands"
  
